commit.title: Renaming nanoPG to microPG.
commit.message:
Renaming nanoPG to microPG.

This is to be consistent with what the preference panel displays (namely μpG).

Maybe this should be the other way round and do a renaming in the
preference panel. In particular, this commit shall induce an
incompatibility from a version of CoqIDE to the other because of the
change of name of the option in coqiderc.
